.SH "Detailed Description"
.PP 
\fBBlockFilterIndex\fP is used to store and retrieve block filters, hashes, and headers for a range of blocks by height\&. An index is constructed for each supported filter type with its own database (ie\&. filter data for different types are stored in separate databases)\&.

.PP
This index is used to serve BIP 157 net requests\&. 
